author: hwright
msg: Extend the changelist-filtering ability to the libsvn_wc-external node walker,
and use it for out changelist getter.
(svn_wc__node_walk_children): Add param, and pass it down the stack.
(crawl_entries): Don't filter via changelist in the walker.
just don't bother filtering on it.
(svn_client_get_changelists): Use the walker to filter based on changelist.

msg: HDFS-1842. Handle editlog opcode conflict with 0.20.203 during upgrade, by throwing an error to indicate the editlog needs to be empty. Contributed by Suresh Srinivas.
